description:
A warm, spacious and cozy apartment with a trendy yet modern look and feel. The apartment features a 50' and 42'  flat screen TVs, queen and full size beds, cable, surround sound, a ceiling fan, a fireplace (not operational) a love seat, a recliner, a glow in the dark fish tank, and a professional looking work area. You'll be 5 minutes from the  Z, J, A and C train and lest than 30 minutes from time square. Lot's of great hangout spots are within walking distance as well.

The apartment is featured in Will Smith's new movie Collateral Beauty. Parts of the movie was shot in the park directly across the street from the apartment.

Entire Apartment.

I'll be in and out but at your service if you need me.

Beautiful and diverse neighborhood with lots of trees.

The A, C, Z and J trains are lest than 5 minutes away.
